n":0},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Last virtue to lose in your religion is prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe first thing you will lose in your religion is trust, and the final thing you will lose is prayer.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Shih\u0101b 216 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26500,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/06\/11\/i-leave-you-protection-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":40741,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Farewell: I leave you to the protection of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 11, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Salim reported: Ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, would say to a man if he intended to travel, \u201cI bid you farewell as the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would bid farewell. The Prophet would say: I leave you under the protection of Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11644,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/22\/do-not-reciprocate-treachery\/","url_meta":{"origin":40741,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Trusts: Fulfill trusts, do not reciprocate betrayal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, p